         <div n="13">
            <head>A TEI conformant document (2017 version) </head>
            <list>
               <item>is a well formed XML document; and </item>
               <item>is valid against one or more schemas, which may be either a TEI subset or
                  a TEI extension; and </item>
               <item>uses elements from the TEI namespace 
                   as defined by the TEI Guidelines; and </item>
               <item>fully documents its use of the TEI 
                  by means of a TEI-conformant
                  ODD vel sim. </item>
            </list>
